20.3.3 OEGetCovalentRadius 
 

 
 OEGetCovalentRadius  returns the covalent radius of an element,
as parameterized by the Cambridge Crystallographic Database (CCD).
Currently, this table contains values for the organic subset of
elements, with inorganic and unparameterized elements returning the
value 0.0f.

  

  
          
     
        
